-- Comments start with two dashes
-- A conversation part type is given by :
-- The types are: :Name :Health :Intro :Hint :Taunt :Response
-- Intro: A short introduction introducing the character
-- Hint: Give the user information about how to beat this character
-- Taunt: Character taunts player, improves his happiness (health)
-- Response: Character's responses to player's taunts

-- Example
:Name Ralphie
:Health 1000


